</P>
<P>
   NEW YORK: Hoffman said.
</P>
<P>
   A8371 BC-SINATRA-IMITATOR-ART-580(2TAKES)-NYT 646 21:38 U A
</P>
<P>
   A LIFELONG FAN BRINGS SINATRA'S STYLE TO A MANHATTAN NIGHTCLUB
</P>
<P>
   A8370 BC-FAULDER-EXECUTION17-COX 787 21:38 U A
</P>
<P>
   A8345 BC-EXP-BEARSTEARNS-SEC-TALKS-NYT 389 21:21 U A
