<HEADLINE>
CLINTON SAYS MILOSEVIC IS SAFE FROM ARREST INSIDE SERBIA 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEWART M. POWELL  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
