   WITH
</P>
<P>
   SHAVING-TIPS _ A review of the just-published ``A Closer Shave:
Man's Daily Search for Perfection'' by Wallace Pinfold. Pulls out
little known facts about shaving today and through history.
(Walton, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Embargoed for Sunday, June 20.
</P>
