<HEADLINE>
FACTS HAZY ABOUT EPIC GUNFIGHT AT OK CORRAL  
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By CLAY THOMPSON  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
