<P>
   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS (e) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MEDIA-NOTES (Evanston, Ill.) &UR;  &LR; -- He was not exactly a household
word, at least not until February when the media picked up the
story of Anthony Porter, a man who was sprung after 17 years on
death row. By Mark Jurkowitz.
