6-17 -- A Serbian farming family stowing their hogs in the trunk of
their automobile as they flee Podujevo, Kosovo. Kosovo Serbs are
packing up their belongings and filling the roads that lead out of
the province. (Alan Chin/New York Times Photo)
</P>
