Galdi handed keys to 28 new BMWs to company workers; under a new
company policy, every employee on the job at least a year gets a
leased BMW, plus fully paid insurance. Turnover has been such that
of 57 workers, only half qualified. But the other half can taste
it. (Dith Pran/New York Times Photo) LITE
