<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-17 22:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9948 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AIRLINE-SERVICE-NYT &LR;      06-17 0831
